Enterprise-Grade Security for the Digital Age

Our purpose is to build a safer, simpler digital future for everyone

Cyber XYZ safeguards people's most important data, wherever they use it. We make it easier for people and companies to stay safe online, so everyone can work, play, and stay productive - without worrying about their security or privacy.

Our history

Started by two friends in 2024, Cyber XYZ was founded on the belief that security is inherently a human challenge, and can only be truly solved with a human-centric approach to product design.

Cyber XYZ is now powered by a global team of over 1,300 people. Our relentless focus on user experience, privacy, and security make Cyber XYZ the world's most trusted and loved identity security company.

Location & Hours

Our cybersecurity experts are available 24/7 to protect your business and respond to security incidents.
